      • canModify

        default boolean canModify(IMember member)
        Check if this role can modify attributes of another member. A role can only manage members that have a lower role. Note that this method does not checks the role's permissions.
        Parameters:
        member - The member to check with.
        Returns:
        True if the other member is modifiable.

      • canModify

        default boolean canModify(IRole role)
        Check if this role can modify attributes of another role. A role can only manages roles that are lower than this role. Note that this method checks the role's permissions. (Manage Roles permission)
        Parameters:
        role - The role to check with.
        Returns:
        True if the role is modifiable.
